ZH: 我向你道歉，我错了。
EN: I apologize to you, I was wrong.

ZH: 对不起，我没有听清楚你说的话。
EN: I'm sorry, I didn't hear what you said clearly.

ZH: 我向你诚挚道歉。
EN: I sincerely apologize to you.

ZH: 对不起，我让你失望了。
EN: I'm sorry, I disappointed you.

ZH: 我向你们所有人道歉，我犯了一个大错误。
EN: I apologize to all of you, I made a big mistake.

ZH: 对不起，我给你带来了麻烦。
EN: I'm sorry, I caused trouble for you.

ZH: 我对我的行为感到后悔，向你道歉。
EN: I regret my actions and apologize to you.

ZH: 对不起，我忘了答应你的事情。
EN: I'm sorry, I forgot about what I promised you.

ZH: 我做错了事情，我向你道歉。
EN: I did something wrong, I apologize to you.

ZH: 对不起，我对你的态度不好。
EN: I'm sorry, I had a bad attitude towards you.

ZH: 我真心感到抱歉，希望你能原谅我。
EN: I genuinely feel sorry, I hope you can forgive me.

ZH: 对不起，我伤害了你的感情。
EN: I'm sorry, I hurt your feelings.

ZH: 我知道我做得不对，我向你道歉。
EN: I know I did wrong, I apologize to you.

ZH: 对不起，我没有考虑周全。
EN: I'm sorry, I didn't think things through.

ZH: 我向你深深道歉，我懂得自己的错。
EN: I deeply apologize to you, I understand my mistake.

ZH: 对不起，我没能按时完成工作。
EN: I'm sorry, I didn't complete the work on time.

ZH: 我向你真诚致歉，因为我的愚蠢行为。
EN: I sincerely apologize to you for my foolish behavior.

ZH: 对不起，我伤害了你的感情，我会努力弥补。
EN: I'm sorry, I hurt your feelings, I will try to make it up to you.

ZH: 我向你道歉，我实在不该那样说。
EN: I apologize to you, I shouldn't have said that.

ZH: 对不起，我造成的困扰给你带来了不便。
EN: I'm sorry, the trouble I caused brought inconvenience to you.
